nodes.text: A commoner inhabited Anchorhead during the time of the Galactic Civil War.

During 1 ABY, a commoner resided in Anchorhead on Tatooine. During their time in Anchorhead, the commoner became involved with the squill industry, and employed the help of a spacer to eliminate squill in their respective lair.

This commoner served as a herald quest Non-Player Character (NPC) in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. In the game, players could enter a dialogue with the commoner concerning the squill industry. After agreeing to help the commoner, players would be given a waypoint to the squill cave on Tatooine. However, aside from receiving the waypoint, players were not required to fulfill any specific objective. Speaking to the commoner simply allowed players to discover the location.
